    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "translated": "When we were recording this song... it's very refreshing, but"
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "translated": "in the A and B sections, there's a lot of hesitation."
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "translated": "I was told to convey a sense of bewilderment and not to sing it too strongly."
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "translated": "And for the chorus... how should I put it..."
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "translated": "I was told to sing with a sense of transparency, and we all sang it together."
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "translated": "Personally, I love the lyric about having apple pie on a day of celebration so much."
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "translated": "In the lyrics written for us..."
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "translated": "there haven't been many times where a character's favorite thing is mentioned so directly."
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "translated": "."
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "translated": "Does it feel like her?"
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "translated": "I had that image... I remember it feeling quite fresh."
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "translated": "That part just keeps playing in my head. I personally really like it."
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "translated": "And also, I think it was on the Master difficulty chart?"
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "translated": "An apple pie appears in it."
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "translated": "They worked hard to make it look like an apple pie, a really big apple pie."
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "translated": "It was like, 'Oh, it's an apple pie!' and I played it a bit."
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "translated": "If you're curious, please try playing the Master difficulty."
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "translated": "I wonder if Shiho's ramen will show up eventually? Do you think so?"
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "translated": "Would Shiho even get such a poppy song?"
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "translated": "But I'd certainly like to see it."
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "translated": "Try playing the Master chart."
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "translated": "..."
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "translated": "The Master chart should be available to play right away, so"
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "translated": "please give it a try."
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "translated": "Shiho and ramen... I can't quite imagine it."
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "translated": "A little..."
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "translated": "Do they want us to play it that much?"
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "translated": "Or maybe they want it to be metal?"
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "translated": "Like 'chugga-chugga-chugga-chugga.'"
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "translated": "D-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d!"
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "translated": "Slap bass is impossible... true."
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "translated": "The steam from the ramen would be all zigzaggy."
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "translated": "Wow, you have a great imagination."
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "translated": "In this way, characters' favorite things might be included in the future,"
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "translated": "so I'm looking forward to it."
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "translated": "I'm also happy to see Saki-chan in her outfit here."
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "translated": "I also noticed that the heart marks and logos were different for each of them."
